_sText: ZM_OFFIZ0R_V1 by 2ToW *** Info: The map is just larger thank huge! CTs spawn in the office at the back and Ts spawn near the door where u can get outside. Outside are has 1 secret spot. Office = Cading Outside area = climbing and cading Warehouse = Climbing and cading (more climbing!) *** New on v2: - Added more than 25 rooms. - Optimized as much as i can.
